show.title: Mr. Ji, See Clearly, I'm Your Bodyguard
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा 
https://links.kukufm.com/vuUMCY
show.description: Jeni’s family forces her into an engagement with a stranger. Refusing to be a pawn, she escapes before the wedding, determined to reclaim her freedom. But her defiance turns dangerous—her own family hunts her down, ready to drag her back. To survive, Jeni disguises herself as a man and takes an unexpected job as a bodyguard to a wealthy businessman. She has no idea he’s the same man she was supposed to marry.
